      "role": "user",
      "content": "really? i was reading some health blog saying that as long as you dont drink the juice at the exact same time as the pill, it doesn't matter. like if i have the juice in the morning and take my pill at night, it's totally fine right? it seems like a bit of an exaggeration to say it's dangerous.",
